Enum Bitboard.AntiDiagonal

  • Object
    • Enum<Bitboard.AntiDiagonal>
      • Bitboard.AntiDiagonal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Bitboard.AntiDiagonal>
    Enclosing class:
    Bitboard

    public static enum Bitboard.AntiDiagonal
extends Enum<Bitboard.AntiDiagonal>
    An enum type for the 15 anti-diagonals of a chess board. Each constant has a field that contains a long with only the bitboard on indices of the squares falling on the diagonal set.
    Author:
    Viktor
